<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Hasil Broadcast Bot - Berani Cerdas</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>body { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); }</style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">
  <div class="w-full max-w-3xl">
    <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-2xl">
      
      <div class="mb-6 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-2">📣 Hasil Broadcast Bot</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Laporan pengiriman broadcast menggunakan bot Telegram resmi.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3 mb-6 text-center">
        <div class="rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5">
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-semibold">Total Target</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900"><%= users.length %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5">
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-semibold">Terkirim</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-600"><%= success %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5">
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-semibold">Gagal</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-red-600"><%= failed %></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 p-6 mb-6 text-slate-700">
        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">💡 Informasi Audit</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Broadcast dijalankan menggunakan sistem antrean pasif. Hanya pengguna Telegram yang terdaftar sebagai <em>subscriber</em> aktif di database Supabase yang menerima pesan ini. Riwayat aksi ini telah otomatis dicatat ke dalam tabel <strong>broadcast_logs</strong>.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex items-center justify-between border-t border-blue-200/60 pt-3 text-sm">
          <span>Persentase Keberhasilan System:</span>
          <span class="font-bold text-blue-700"><%= successRate %>%</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-3 grid-cols-2 border-t border-slate-100 pt-6">
        <a href="/admin" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 px-4 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-white transition hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-purple-700 shadow-md hover:scale-[1.01] active:scale-[0.99]">
          🏠 Kembali ke Dashboard
        </a>
        <a href="/admin/logout" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-red-50 hover:bg-red-100 px-4 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-red-600 transition border border-red-200/50 shadow-sm">
          🚪 Logout
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>